# Project

This project was made by Tomer Kordonsky.

## Installation

```bash

```

## Running

```bash
uvicorn app:main
```

## Endpoints 
- drivers_by_season/{season} -> Returns a json file of drivers sorted by the wins in the requested season
- seasons_all_time_ranking/{season} -> Returns a json file of seasons with the top 3 drivers in each season
- driver_profile/{driver_id_or_name} -> Returns a specific driver (by id/name) with all of his races sorted by date from newest to the oldest